snippet.title: Mistover - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
MISTOVER, the dungeon crawler RPG from KRAFTON Game Union (PUBG) is headed to PS4 on October 10, 2019! Play the demo now!

More info at: https://playmistover.com/home
Follow MISTOVER at: https://twitter.com/MISTOVER_EN

1st gameplay trailer!
Watch the Expedition Corps explore the Misfortunate Mist through an ever-changing dungeon through the Pillar of Despair and battle monsters with a strategy focused turn-based combat system.
